channel.itunes:summary: Come and have a taste of our world with your hosts, Rockliffe & Dmak. They will take you through all the news, features, events and interviews as well a healthy slice of banter and random fun. With a side order of the best in electro, trance, tech-trance and techno, marinated with guest mixes, mini mix mash up's and much much more, your audio taste buds will tingling with excitement! Work Hard, Play Harder with The Official HarderFaster.net Podcast.
